'''''A Warrior's Views''''' was a [[book]] penned by [[Galgarr Thormspur]] and published in [[400 DR]].

{{quote|''Choosing what road to walk in life is a luxury given to few in [[Faerûn]]. Perhaps lack of practice is why so many who do have that choice make such a [[god]]s-[[curse]]d mess of it.''|Excerpt from the ''A Warrior's Views''}}
